{"word":"H6307 - פַּדָּן - Paddân - pad-dawn' - Padan","slug":"H6307","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פַּדָּן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Paddân"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pad-dawn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Padan"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05DF; &#x05D0;&#x05E8;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05DF; - padda&#x0302;n  paddan 'a&#x0306;ra&#x0302;m</b> - <i>pad-dawn', pad-dan' ar-awm'</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>extend</i>; a <i>plateau</i>; or the second form which is from the same and <a href=\"#/H758\">H758</a>; the <i>table land of Aram</i>; <i>Paddan</i> or <i>Paddan-Aram</i>, a region of Syria: - Padan, Padan-aram."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6299\">H6299</a>, <a href=\"#/H6300\">H6300</a>, <a href=\"#/H6301\">H6301</a>, <a href=\"#/H6302\">H6302</a>, <a href=\"#/H6303\">H6303</a>, <a href=\"#/H6304\">H6304</a>, <a href=\"#/H6305\">H6305</a>, <a href=\"#/H6306\">H6306</a>"}]}